03E3                             ;MEANS THAT THE POSSIBLE ZERO CONDITION MUST BY DETECTED AND THE TABLE ENTRY CALCULATOR 
03E3                             ;SECTION SKIPPED OVER. WHEN ACCESSING THE DISPLAY TABLES, THE MENU ENTRY NUMBER IS 
